verbLexeme: 1. To violently force someone to have sex with you when they do not want to. English = rape.
nominalLexeme: 1. The act of violently forcing someone to have sex with you when they do not want to. English = rape.
2. A person, usually a man, who violently forces other people, usually women, to have sex with him when they do not want to. English = rapist.
